             SOC 117 - Statistics for Social Scientists
           </dt> 
           <dt id="9113" data-termcode="" data-subjectcode="SOC" data-coursenumber="201" data-credits="" data-title="Contemporary Social Problems" class="nodescription">
             SOC 201 - Contemporary Social Problems
