             SOC 210 - Sociological Research Methods
           </dt> 
           <dt id="9139" data-termcode="" data-subjectcode="SOC" data-coursenumber="217" data-credits="" data-title="The Sociology of Management" class="nodescription">
             SOC 217 - The Sociology of Management
           </dt> 
           <dt id="9116" data-termcode="" data-subjectcode="SOC" data-coursenumber="225" data-credits="" data-title="Sociology of Gender" class="nodescription">
             SOC 225 - Sociology of Gender
           </dt> 
           <dt id="9117" data-termcode="" data-subjectcode="SOC" data-coursenumber="226" data-credits="" data-title="Sociology of Race and Ethnicity" class="nodescription">
             SOC 226 - Sociology of Race and Ethnicity
           </dt> 
           <dt id="9118" data-termcode="" data-subjectcode="SOC" data-coursenumber="227" data-credits="" data-title="Sociology of Families" class="nodescription">
             SOC 227 - Sociology of Families
